trans-unit.source: Provides methods for working with the runtime metadata for an activity tree.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder metoder for å arbeide med kjøretiden metadataene for en aktivitetstre.

trans-unit.source: Caches the runtime metadata for the specified activity tree.
trans-unit.target: Bufrer runtime metadataene for den angitte aktivitetstre.

trans-unit.source: The root activity of the activity tree.
trans-unit.target: Root aktiviteten i aktivitetstreet.

trans-unit.source: Caches the runtime metadata for the specified activity tree using the specified environment.
trans-unit.target: Bufrer runtime metadataene for den angitte aktiviteten-tre ved hjelp av det angitte miljøet.

trans-unit.source: The root activity of the activity tree.
trans-unit.target: Root aktiviteten i aktivitetstreet.

trans-unit.source: The environment associated with the activity tree.
trans-unit.target: Miljøet knyttet til aktivitetstreet.

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the service can include idle activities.
trans-unit.target: Angir om tjenesten kan inneholde inaktiv aktiviteter.

trans-unit.source: The activity.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the service can include idle activities; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis tjenesten kan inneholde inaktiv aktiviteter. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> that represents all activities associated with the input activity.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> som representerer alle aktiviteter tilknyttet inndata aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: The enumeration contains all child activities, delegate handlers, variable defaults, and argument expressions.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen inneholder alle underordnede aktiviteter representanten behandlingsprogrammer, variabelen standarder og argumentet uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: If the input activity is `null`, an <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den angitte aktiviteten `null`, en <xref:System.ArgumentNullException>forårsakes.</xref:System.ArgumentNullException>

trans-unit.source: The activity tree must remain unmodified and <xref:System.Activities.WorkflowInspectionServices.CacheMetadata%2A> must not be called while the tree is being enumerated or else an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> is thrown when <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitetstreet må være uendret og <xref:System.Activities.WorkflowInspectionServices.CacheMetadata%2A>må ikke kalles mens treet nummererte eller andre en <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>oppstår når er <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>kalles.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> </xref:System.InvalidOperationException> </xref:System.Activities.WorkflowInspectionServices.CacheMetadata%2A>

trans-unit.source: Calling this method causes a full cache metadata to occur.
trans-unit.target: Kaller denne metoden fører til at et fullstendig hurtigbufferen metadata kan utføres.

trans-unit.source: If you make changes to the workflow after calling this method, you must call the <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices> <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A> method after making the changes in order to re-cache the metadata.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du endrer arbeidsflyten etter kalle denne metoden, må du kaller den <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices> <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A>metoden etter endringer for å hurtigbufre på nytt metadataene.</xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices>

trans-unit.source: The root activity.
trans-unit.target: Root-aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: An enumeration that represents all activities associated with the input activity.
trans-unit.target: En opplisting som representerer alle aktiviteter tilknyttet inndata aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the implementation version of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Henter versjonen til aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: The activity.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: The implementation version of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Implementering versjonen av aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: Returns the activity with the specified id from the specified activity tree.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer aktiviteten med angitt id fra angitte aktivitetstreet.

trans-unit.source: The activity tree to search.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitetstreet for å søke.

trans-unit.source: The identifier of the activity to find.
trans-unit.target: Identifikatoren for aktivitet for å finne.

trans-unit.source: The specified activity if found; otherwise, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte aktiviteten hvis finnes. Ellers en <xref:System.ArgumentException>forårsakes.</xref:System.ArgumentException>
